  <summary date="2020-03-23T04:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">State Housing Relief Act of 2020

This bill provides funds for&#160;assistance to homeowners to prevent mortgage defaults, foreclosures, and displacements of individuals and families experiencing financial hardship&#160;after January 21, 2020. The Department of the Treasury must disburse the funds to state housing finance agencies for the provision of such assistance.</summary>
